# 5. Running JavaScript Programs

# Method 1: Using Browser

## Example HTML File

```html id="r8y5u2"
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>JavaScript Example</title>
</head>

<body>

<script>
alert("Welcome to JavaScript");
</script>

</body>
</html>
```

---

## Steps

1. Save file as `index.html`
2. Open file in browser
3. Browser executes JavaScript automatically

