└── app.js
```

---

# Explanation

| File       | Purpose              |
| ---------- | -------------------- |
| index.html | Structure of webpage |
| style.css  | Styling              |
| app.js     | JavaScript logic     |

---

# 7. Adding JavaScript to HTML

# Internal JavaScript

JavaScript written inside HTML file.

```html id="b2p7m5"
<script>
console.log("Internal JavaScript");
</script>
```

---

# External JavaScript

JavaScript stored in separate `.js` file.

```html id="q4n8t1"
<script src="app.js"></script>
```

---

# Advantages of External JavaScript

* Better code organization
* Easy maintenance
* Reusable code
* Faster page loading

